        "comment": "Great app which I have used almost everyday. While I do like it, there could be one additional feature to improve the experience. I often find myself pinning two of the same pictures to one board without being notified of the duplicate. The app will tell me in cases of the same exact post however, if there is one picture posted by two or more different people then i won't be notified. Perhaps the app could scan the pictures in my board and see if I had previously pinned anything that looks identical in order to reduce duplicates.",
